            "name": "Giant Bone Skipper",
            "type": "section",
            "text": "While less common than the smaller variety, giant bone skippers are the stuff of nightmares for morticians and graveyard keepers.<br/><br/><b><u><a aonid=\"5\" game-obj=\"Skills\" general=\"true\">Recall Knowledge - Animal</a></u> (<u><a aonid=\"10\" game-obj=\"Skills\">Nature</a></u>)</b>: DC 25",
